title: Programs and addons for FS2004.
description:
I made a selection of some addons more important than not missing here in my FS2004.
I hope you enjoy.
 
Aircraft: Iris BAE Harrier - The only with vertical takeoff and landing for the FS.
 
Updates important for the FS9.
 
Miscellaneous: 
Texture grass and ground - reflections for aircraft - xenon2 - Samoshin trees - Ultimate water - Zinertek world environment - Jetsmoke - Pushback (Panel) - reduced callouts - fscontrail - engineexhaustsystem - Igfly walk and follow - bluer tire smoke.
 
Scenery: Meigs Field.
